These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
City: prague, liverpool, boston, hannover
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to hannover##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| City   | prague | hannover | liverpool | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani, oliveros, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the swisher-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | bongani | swisher | baccarat | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, zombie, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | fantasy | zombie | drama |

 #################################

 
