.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, singing
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3   |    4     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | gardening | singing |

